Toban's key is given by Og in the Watchtower quest to open the chest near Gorad. After opening the chest you will find Toban's gold and the key will consumed.


Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
5 December 2006
(update)

The "Drop" option was replaced with a "Destroy" option.

30 January 2006
(update)
  • The item was renamed from "Toban key" to "Toban's key".
  • The item's examine was changed from undefined ("It's a Toban key.") to "Formerly the property of Toban the ogre."
